summary.label:
Handwrite the things to do in a fast and easy way.

Features: 
- choose the color and size of the brush; 
- add a new task in the list; 
- edit the name of the task (tap on the row); 
- change the position of the task into the list (long press on the row);
- change the height of the row;
- select/deselect the task;
- delete the task from the list once you have done; 
- share the list.
